title: Fortinet FortiGate IPS: Detection and Blocking rate
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/fortinet
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the intrusion detection and blocking rate of FortiGate
 IPS systems. It goes {WARN} or {CRIT} if the detection rate exceeds user-
 configurable levels (rule "Fortinet FortiGate IPS Detections"). The default
 thresholds are 100 and 300 detections per second.

item:
 Internal virtual domain index.

discovery:
 One service is created per virtual domain.
